'''瑪格麗特·「瑪姬」·哈桑'''（{{lang-en|Margaret "Maggie" Hassan}}（舊姓'''伍德'''（{{lang|en|Wood}}））；{{bd|1958年|2月27日|}}），是一名[[美國|美國]]政治人物與[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]成員<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.wmur.com/article/updated-nh-democrats-to-vote-on-superdelegate-reform-resolution-at-convention/5212154|title=Updated: NH Democrats to vote on superdelegate reform resolution at convention|last=|first=|date=2016-06-16|work=WMUR|access-date=|via=|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814091203/https://www.wmur.com/article/updated-nh-democrats-to-vote-on-superdelegate-reform-resolution-at-convention/5212154|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在2013年當選為{{le|新罕布什爾州州長列表|List of Governors of New Hampshire|第81任}}{{le|新罕布什爾州州長|Governor of New Hampshire}}，並將在2017年就任[[新罕布什爾州|新罕布什爾州]][[美國參議院|資淺參議員]]。

哈桑在[[馬薩諸塞州|馬薩諸塞州]][[波士顿|波士顿]]出生<ref name="bernstein">{{cite news|last1=Bernstein|first1=David|title=A Rumble in the Granite State|url=http://www.bostonmagazine.com/news/article/2016/07/17/new-hampshire-senate-race/|accessdate=2016-07-26|publisher=Boston Magazine|date=July 2016|archive-date=2017-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008201656/http://www.bostonmagazine.com/news/article/2016/07/17/new-hampshire-senate-race/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於[[布朗大学|布朗大学]]畢業、並在1985年取得了[[东北大学法学院|东北大学法学院]][[法律博士|法律博士]]學位<ref name="usa">{{cite news|last1=Gingrich|first1=Drew|title=Profile: New Hampshire Gov.-elect Maggie Hassan|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2012/11/07/hassan-new-hampshire-governor-profile/1690055/#|accessdate=2016-02-08|publisher=USA Today|date=2012-11-07|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114213645/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2012/11/07/hassan-new-hampshire-governor-profile/1690055/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=New Hampshire Governor Maggie Hassan|url=http://www.nga.org/cms/home/governors/current-governors/col2-content/main-content-list/maggie-hassan.html|publisher=National Governors Association|accessdate=2016-02-08|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214651/http://www.nga.org/cms/home/governors/current-governors/col2-content/main-content-list/maggie-hassan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之後在波士顿任職律師和醫療保健主管<ref name="usa"/>。

2002年，她在民主黨領導人徵募下首次參選[[新罕布什爾州參議院|新罕布什爾州參議院]]第二十三選區，同時民主黨也徵募人初選本州聯邦參議院議席<ref name=atlantic>{{cite news|last1=Ball|first1=Molly|title=How She Does It|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2014/04/how-she-does-it/360471/|accessdate=2016-02-08|publisher=The Atlantic|date=2014-04-11|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209201900/https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2014/04/how-she-does-it/360471/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2015/07/harry-reid-final-campaign-119788|title=Harry Reid's final campaign|last=|first=|date=2015-07-07|work=Politico|access-date=|via=|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125033016/https://www.politico.com/story/2015/07/harry-reid-final-campaign-119788|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但她輸給時任參議員羅素·普雷斯科特（{{lang|en|Russell Prescott}}）。2004年她捲土重來終於當選<ref name=":1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=48802 |title=Our Campaigns - NH State Senate 23 Race - November 5, 2002 |access-date=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114213835/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=48802 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=372194 |title=NH State Senate 23 Race - November 7, 2006 |access-date=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114213758/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=372194 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，共連任兩次、任職六年（2005年1月－2010年12月）；自2008年後，哈桑更成為州參議院民主黨{{le|多數黨領袖|Majority leader}}，直到她在2010年失去議席為止。

2011年10月，哈桑宣布{{le|2012年新罕布什爾州州長選舉|New Hampshire gubernatorial election, 2012|參選新罕布什爾州州長}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.seacoastonline.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20111025%2FNEWS%2F111029836%2F-1%2FNEWSMAP |title=Hassan announces run for N.H. governor |access-date=2022-01-16 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912002825/https://www.seacoastonline.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20111025%2FNEWS%2F111029836%2F-1%2FNEWSMAP |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在初選中擊敗前州參議員{{le|傑基·茨雷|Jackie Cilley}}獲得提名<ref>{{cite news|last1=Landrigan|first1=Kevin|title=Hassan, Lamontagne paint each other as extremists day after primary victories|url=http://www.nashuatelegraph.com/news/statenewengland/975135-469/hassan-lamontagne-paint-each-other-as-extremists.html|accessdate=2016-02-08|publisher=Nashua Telegraph|date=2012-09-13|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309080247/http://www.nashuatelegraph.com/news/statenewengland/975135-469/hassan-lamontagne-paint-each-other-as-extremists.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大選中她獲得54.6%選票，壓倒[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]候選人{{le|奧維德·拉蒙塔涅|Ovide Lamontagne}}的42.52%選票當選州長<ref>{{cite news|title=2012 New Hampshire Governor Results|url=http://www.politico.com/2012-election/results/governor/new-hampshire/|accessdate=2016-02-08|publisher=Politico|date=2012-11-19|archive-date=2017-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170615220746/http://www.politico.com/2012-election/results/governor/new-hampshire/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並成為該州繼[[珍妮·沙欣|珍妮·沙欣]]後第二名女州長；其後{{le|2014年新罕布什爾州州長選舉|New Hampshire gubernatorial election, 2014|2014年選舉}}她成功連任州長<ref>{{cite web|title=Governor - 2014 General Election|url=http://sos.nh.gov/Elections/Election_Information/2014_Elections/General_Election/Governor_-_2014_General_Election.aspx?id=8589941820|publisher=New Hampshire Secretary of State|accessdate=2016-02-08|archive-date=2018-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107183406/http://sos.nh.gov/Elections/Election_Information/2014_Elections/General_Election/Governor_-_2014_General_Election.aspx?id=8589941820|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在州長任期內，哈桑曾擔任{{le|民主黨州長協會|Democratic Governors Association}}副主席及[[2016年民主黨全國代表大會|民主黨全國代表大會]][[超级代表|超级代表]]<ref name=":0" />。

2016年11月8日，她在{{le|2016年新罕布什爾州美國參議院議員選舉|United States Senate election in New Hampshire, 2016|2016年美國參議院選舉}}擊敗現任共和黨參議員[[凯利·阿约特|凯利·阿约特]]，當選為新罕布什爾州聯邦參議員<ref name=reelection>{{cite web |title=Hassan Tops Havenstein To Win 2nd Term As NH Governor |url=http://boston.cbslocal.com/2014/11/04/hassan-tops-havenstein-to-win-2nd-term-as-nh-governor |work=CBS News |date=2014-11-05 |accessdate=2016-11-14 |archive-date=2014-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105125049/http://boston.cbslocal.com/2014/11/04/hassan-tops-havenstein-to-win-2nd-term-as-nh-governor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

